text: Gerrit van Voorst (18 July 1910 - 13 November 1986) was a Dutch swimmer. He competed in the men's 4 × 200 metre freestyle relay event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1910 births Category:1986 deaths Category:Dutch male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of the Netherlands Category:Swimmers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Amsterdam Category:Male freestyle swimmers
